replies.body:
Your LP gain/loss amount is due to your low MMR (Match making rating). This means your team is favoured to win the game, this is because the matchmaking system is  testing to see if you can keep your bronze 4 rank. Once you have won enough games, and the system thinks you are in your deserved rank, then you will be match evenly/unfavourably so the system can test if you are ready to go up to the next rank (normal/High MMR). When this happens you will see your LP gain/loss becoming the same or even more Lp for winning.

Focus on improving your game, not your rank. Rank will come when you have improved your game, on the flip side, focusing on your rank will only make you angry/tilt/blame others.
 Good Luck{{summoner:31}}
